<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:08:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列的民主尚未得救：司法政变最终如何获胜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-democracy-hasnt-been-saved-how-the-judicial-coup-eventually-prevailed/0000018d-fa9e-d1c2-af9f-ffbfe72b0000</link><description>司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 公布削弱司法机构的计划 14 个月后，尽管高等法院的一项裁决拯救了合理性标准，但该标准已被削弱，法院现在拥有保守派多数</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-democracy-hasnt-been-saved-how-the-judicial-coup-eventually-prevailed/0000018d-fa9e-d1c2-af9f-ffbfe72b0000</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，非利士人崇拜希腊母神，在邪教中使用毒品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/philistines-worshipped-greek-mother-goddess-used-drugs-in-cult-study-shows/0000018e-09d6-d5ee-a78e-39d60d5b0000</link><description>对圣经巨人歌利亚的出生地迦特神庙中植物遗骸的分析表明，非利士宗教包括外国和当地迦南仪式的混合体</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/philistines-worshipped-greek-mother-goddess-used-drugs-in-cult-study-shows/0000018e-09d6-d5ee-a78e-39d60d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的残酷性被其权力下放所掩盖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-cruelty-is-concealed-by-its-decentralization/0000018e-0970-d857-adff-cff9519e0000</link><description>就像一种看不见的化学元素一样，以色列的残暴行为已经在时间和空间中蔓延，由于其同谋者数不胜数且大多匿名，因此以色列的残暴行为一直处于隐蔽状态。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-cruelty-is-concealed-by-its-decentralization/0000018e-0970-d857-adff-cff9519e0000</guid></item><item><title>WZO 的自由派集团声称在年度会议上战胜了极端分子和福音派</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/wzos-liberal-bloc-claims-victory-over-extremists-and-evangelicals-at-annual-confab/0000018e-0984-d3bd-afce-b9c7952e0000</link><description>世界犹太复国主义组织代表通过决议，使奥兹玛·耶胡迪特等极右团体难以竞选世界犹太复国主义大会，也使那些属于其他宗教的人难以以“自我认同的犹太人”身份投票</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/wzos-liberal-bloc-claims-victory-over-extremists-and-evangelicals-at-annual-confab/0000018e-0984-d3bd-afce-b9c7952e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家庭在议会举行无声游行，并附上被俘亲人的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-families-hold-silent-march-at-knesset-with-photos-of-captive-loved-ones/0000018e-0955-d5ee-a78e-39d7e98c0000</link><description>在以色列议会关于人质家庭健康问题的会议上，与会者猛烈抨击了以色列政府对人质危机的处理方式，其中一位与会者表示，“日子一天天过去，什么也没有发生”，并补充道，“这些家庭都快被淹死了”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-families-hold-silent-march-at-knesset-with-photos-of-captive-loved-ones/0000018e-0955-d5ee-a78e-39d7e98c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列对约旦河西岸首都拉马拉进行了多年来最大规模的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/israel-carries-out-largest-raid-in-west-bank-capital-ramallah-in-years-palestinians-say/0000018e-08e9-dbc9-a38f-b8fb3c2d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报告称，加沙战争期间西岸暴力事件激增，以色列军队在连夜突袭中杀死了一名 16 岁男孩</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/israel-carries-out-largest-raid-in-west-bank-capital-ramallah-in-years-palestinians-say/0000018e-08e9-dbc9-a38f-b8fb3c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，被绑架以色列士兵的父亲发现了令人不安的细节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-father-discovers-disturbing-details-on-october-7/0000018e-04f2-d3bd-afce-b5f3c50d0000</link><description>一辆装备精良、防护严密的坦克是如何在10月7日一早落入哈马斯手中，导致以色列士兵被杀和绑架的？</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/kidnapped-israeli-soldiers-father-discovers-disturbing-details-on-october-7/0000018e-04f2-d3bd-afce-b5f3c50d0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，许多以色列人认为内塔尼亚胡因政治原因拖延人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/plurality-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-stalling-on-hostage-deal-over-politics-poll-shows/0000018e-086a-d5ee-a78e-38ea87de0000</link><description>民意调查显示，73% 的世俗以色列犹太人支持目前正在讨论的释放人质和停火协议，而传统犹太人和极端正统犹太人的这一比例分别为 52% 和 24%</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:37:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/plurality-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-stalling-on-hostage-deal-over-politics-poll-shows/0000018e-086a-d5ee-a78e-38ea87de0000</guid></item><item><title>朱迪亚沙漠发现稀有硬币，命名为巴尔·科赫巴领导人“牧师以利亚泽”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article/rare-coin-naming-bar-kochba-leader-eleazer-the-priest-found-in-judean-desert/0000018e-089e-d5ee-a78e-38de5ddd0000</link><description>这枚硬币上刻有公元 132 年的日期，并用古希伯来文字刻有牧师的名字。它似乎是从以色列死海的一个山洞里掉下来的，犹太叛乱分子一直躲在那里躲避罗马人——他们手中的标枪可能是偷来的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-04/ty-article/rare-coin-naming-bar-kochba-leader-eleazer-the-priest-found-in-judean-desert/0000018e-089e-d5ee-a78e-38de5ddd0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯狙击手使用公开出售给伊朗的美制瞄准镜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-snipers-using-u-s-made-sights-sold-openly-to-iran/0000018e-05e6-d3bd-afce-b5e7279a0000</link><description>从加沙缴获的狙击步枪上发现了一家在伊朗有官方经销商的美国公司生产的望远镜瞄准镜。该公司指控中国诈骗</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-snipers-using-u-s-made-sights-sold-openly-to-iran/0000018e-05e6-d3bd-afce-b5e7279a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军官员：如果不改变加沙的援助分配，杀戮场面将重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officials-warn-without-method-of-aid-distribution-gaza-killings-will-repeat/0000018e-06fb-d5ee-a78e-36fb21dd0000</link><description>100 多名巴勒斯坦人在等待人道主义援助时被杀，以色列国防军官员敦促政府考虑在没有哈马斯参与的情况下分发援助物资的新方式，包括通过巴勒斯坦商人或海上</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officials-warn-without-method-of-aid-distribution-gaza-killings-will-repeat/0000018e-06fb-d5ee-a78e-36fb21dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将人道主义援助作为加沙的战略武器，但没有制定战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-using-humanitarian-aid-as-a-strategic-weapon-without-a-strategy/0000018e-068b-d3bd-afce-b7cb1a610000</link><description>援助不仅以卡车数量或分配的资金来衡量，还需要基于交战各方之间协议的受保护道路和安全区域。但这些协议并不是免费的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-using-humanitarian-aid-as-a-strategic-weapon-without-a-strategy/0000018e-068b-d3bd-afce-b7cb1a610000</guid></item><item><title>救援部门称，黎巴嫩反坦克导弹造成 1 人死亡、7 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon-gantz-kicks-off-u-s-visit/0000018e-0776-d822-a9ce-7ff77a760000</link><description>以色列北部反坦克导弹造成一人死亡、七人受伤 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：释放人质，下周末可能达成停火协议 ■ 部长本尼·甘茨在华盛顿与美国高级官员开始一轮会谈 ■哈马斯卫生部称加沙死亡人数上升至 30,534 人</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:14:25 GMT</pubDate><gui