aeli-strike-killed-them-both/0000018e-055c-d3bd-afce-b5dff6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</link><description>中士。来自佩塔提克瓦的 33 岁丹尼斯·叶基莫夫 (Dennis Yekimov) 少校于周六在汗尤尼斯被杀。 “我再也见不到你了，只在照片里。”你是世界上最好的父亲，”他的小女儿哀悼道</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯拒绝透露人质姓名后，以色列抵制在开罗举行的加沙谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</link><description>以色列安全内阁的消息人士批评内塔尼亚胡要求获得在与哈马斯达成协议时释放的活着人质的完整名单。一位人士表示，“这不需要成为推进谈判的障碍”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</guid></item><item><title>正确阅读民意调查：大多数美国人支持以色列而不是哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</link><description>如果以色列人没有在以色列的每个新闻周期中一次又一次地被告知，反以色列、支持哈马斯的情绪正在席卷美国，吓坏那里的犹太人和以色列人呢？</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</guid></item><item><title>2500万年前的一次突变如何让人类失去了尾巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</link><description>一项新的研究探讨了人类尾巴缺失背后的神秘遗传机制，一些人认为这可能是类人猿两足行走的关键</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article-magazine/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>